1936;;The Man in the Mirror;;British;;Maurice Elvey;;Edward Everett Horton, Genevieve Tobin;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Man_in_the_Mirror_(1936_film);;A withdrawn, mild mannered man is surprised when his reflection in the mirror steps out of the mirror and tells him he is his alter ego, the kind of man he wishes he was. The man-in-the-mirror then begins to live the wild life that the man had always dreamed of.